<h2 style="margin-top:0;color:#111827;">New Verification Code</h2>
<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;">
  Hi
  {{firstName}}, you requested a new verification code. Use the code below to
  verify your email address.
</p>

<div style="margin:28px 0;text-align:center;">
  <div
    style="display:inline-block;background:#f3f4f6;border:1px dashed #d1d5db;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 32px;"
  >
    <p
      style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;"
    >Verification Code</p>
    <p
      style="margin:0;font-size:36px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:8px;color:#111827;"
    >{{verificationCode}}</p>
  </div>
  <p style="margin:10px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;">This code expires in
    {{expiresIn}}.</p>
</div>

<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;">
  If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
<p style="margin-top:32px;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;">
  Need help? Visit our
  <a href="#" style="color:#4f46e5;">support center</a>.
</p>